After [[Rom (Earth-616)|Rom]] and [[Brandy Clark (Earth-616)|Brandy Clark]] of [[Earth]] had two sons, [[Balin (Earth-616)|Balin]] and [[Tristan (Earth-616)|Tristan]], their children took up the legacy and become part of a new generation of [[Spaceknights (Galadorian) (Earth-616)|Spaceknights]].{{r|Spaceknights Vol 1 1}}

They would come face to face with the menace of the [[Wraithknights (Earth-616)|Wraithknights]]. While battling this new foe, a [[Deathwing]] was summoned. While trying to find a way to combat the Deathwing, Axadar suddenly appeared to Tristan and bonded with him. He then destroyed the Deathwing.{{r|Spaceknights Vol 1 5}}
